Class PreDefinedContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.content.PreDefinedContent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UIGenerator, XMLGenerator, Contexed

    public class PreDefinedContent
extends java.lang.Object
implements Contexed, XMLGenerator, UIGenerator
    A XMLPrinter containing pre-defined content from a message bundle. This is to allow pre-defined content to be added to a ContentBuilder. The message text is allowed to contain raw HTML formatting
